    "created_at": "2016-11-16T08:03:15Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-11-16T08:03:15Z",
    "body": "There is no native progress box, there are only native dialogs with custom progress bar controls. To have this we have to either provide a complete API for creating native UI components, or provide an API to create a custom dialog with a progress bar in it.\n\nThe former is not on our plan, and the latter is simply impossible to satisfy all use cases. So I'm closing this as won't fix.\n"
